casebody.data:
Kenneth COLEMAN, petitioner,
v.
J.F. CARAWAY, Warden. No. 14-7824. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 23, 2015.

Opinion

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Justice KAGANtook no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
